title: Ukraine and Russia negotiators in Turkey reach deal to resume grain exports | DW News
description: After months of global grain shortages, negotiators in Turkey say they've reached a deal to resume grain exports from Ukraine. After hours of negotiations in Istanbul, Turkey's Defence Minister announced Ukraine and Russia had reached an agreement to allow grain shipments through the Black Sea. Turkey and the United Nations helped broker the deal, expected to be signed next week. The deal would end a months-long impasse that's left more than 20 million tons of much-needed grain stuck in Ukrainian ports -- unable to leave because of fighting in the country.|UN Secretary General Antonio Guterres said more work was still needed to finalize the deal, but hailed the breakthrough as a 'critical step forward.'|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #GrainExports

title: Heatwave and blazing wildfires scorch Southern Europe | DW News
description: Temperatures are set to soar across Europe on Wednesday, with France, Britain, Portugal and Spain on high alert over wildfires and public health.|Spain's Health Ministry warned the "intense heat" could affect people's "vital functions" with heatstroke being a possible consequence. On Twitter, the ministry advised citizens to be on the lookout for the warning signs of heatstroke, such as a rapid heart rate, severe headaches or confusion.|Since Sunday, large parts of the Iberian Peninsula have seen temperatures surpassing 40 degrees Celsius (104 Fahrenheit) as firefighters have battled wildfires across Spain and Portugal.|Around 1,500 firefighters were mobilized to put out three wildfires raging for more than 48 hours in central and northern Portugal over the weekend as the country was hit by a heat wave that prompted the government to declare a "state of contingency."|Southern France is currently battling a wildfire that has been raging since Tuesday afternoon, ripping through 800 hectares of pine trees near Bordeaux and forcing 150 residents to evacuate their homes, according to the local fire department.|Near the Dune of Pilat â€” Europe's tallest sand dune â€” another fire tore through 180 hectares of old pine trees, authorities said.|Some 6,000 campers near the dune had to be evacuated from campsites overnight as a precautionary measure, fire department official Lieutenant Colonel David Annotel told local news channel BFMTV.|High temperatures are also anticipated for other parts of western and central Europe in the coming days.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Heatwave #Wildfires #ClimateChange

title: Curse Of Lono: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
description: Bob Boilen | July 14, 2022|The resonant voice of Felix Bechtolsheimer has me obsessed with his band Curse of Lono. For the group's Tiny Desk (home) concert, the six musicians set up shop in the office at Bechtolsheimer's house above his home studio in South London. They begin their set as they do their evocative 2022 album, People In Cars, with the song "Let Your Love Rain Down On Me." Bechtolsheimer's baritone is set against the dreamy wail of the pedal steel as he sings, "I'm gonna make my move, hear the engine roar / Roll the windows down, slam my foot to the floor / Now I'm driving hard in this big machine / When they kill the pain, we'll all get clean." All that angst leads to the chorus which, for me, offers one of the few glimmers of hope: "Let your love rain down on me." This isn't hope-filled, uplifting music; these are dark songs written following the losses of Felix's father, uncle and former girlfriend. That former partner is the subject of the final spine-chilling song. "So Damned Beautiful" tells the tale of her drug-filled weekend affair that ends in tragedy. It's the first duet Felix Bechtolsheimer has written; originally recorded with Tess Parks, it's sung here with Bo Lucas of the Brighton duo Lucas & King. The fragile characters and cinematic storytelling make their impact thanks to a band that knows how to delicately weave its sound and pulsing textures with an underpinning of drama and plenty of open space that leaves me mesmerized.|SET LIST|"Let Your Love Rain Down On Me"|"Steppin' Out"|"So Damned Beautiful"|MUSICIANS|Felix Bechtolsheimer: vocals, guitars|Bo Lucas: vocals|Joe Harvey Whyte: pedal steel|Tom Sansbury: bass, vocals|Chris Jones: drums, percussion|Carlos de los Santos: keys, vocals|CREDITS|Video by Babysweet|Audio by Toby Hulbert|TINY DESK TEAM|Producer: Bob Boilen|Video Producer: Joshua Bryant|Audio Mastering: Josh Rogosin|Tiny Production Team: Bobby Carter, Kara Frame, Joshua Bryant, Michael Zamora, Maia Stern, Ashley Pointer|VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins|Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann|#TinyDesk #NPRMusic #CurseOfLono

title: On cam: Family picnic turns tragic for Indian family in Oman; Father-son drown in huge wave
description: In a tragic incident, three members of a family from Maharashtra's Sangli got swept away off the coast of Salah al-Mughsail in Oman. The unfortunate incident took place on Sunday afternoon when the family of 4 was playing on the beach in Oman. The video of the incident, which is now going viral, shows a violent wave sweeping away 2 kids, following which their father runs to save them. The father and his 6-year-old son have died while search is on for the 9-year-old missing daughter. Watch this video for more details.|#india #picnic #oman #beach #waves #sangli #maharashtra #family #viral

title: The Hero Teacher Who Saved Sir Mo Farah & Changed His Life Gives His First Hand Account | GMB
description: The teacher who rescued Mo Farah from the house where he was being treated as a slave tells GMB how and when he recognised the Olympic champion had the potential to become a top runner. The bombshell revelations that blew open the world record holder's real life have sent shockwaves around the world. title: Bahas Krisis Ekonomi Sri Lanka di G20, Sri Mulyani Pastikan Ekonomi Domestik Cenderung Stabil
description: NUSA DUA BALI, KOMPAS.TV - Dari forum G20 di Bali ada 3 isu ekonomi global yang jadi pokok pembahasan. ||||Namun selain topik utama, ada pula pembahasan mengenai kondisi krisis ekonomi di Sri Lanka.||||Pertemuan sejumlah Menteri Keuangan dan Gubernur Bank Sentral Negara Anggota G20 di Nusa Dua Bali, akan kembali membahas isu-isu tantangan dan risiko ekonomi global.||||Salah satu bahasan yang juga akan dirundingkan adalah kemelut ekonomi di Sri Lanka, dan dampak krisis negara mutiara Samudera Hindia itu, terhadap dunia.||||Baca Juga Menteri Keuangan Ukraina Hadir Virtual di G20, Bahas Imbas Perang Hingga Penerbitan Uang Digital di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308769/menteri-keuangan-ukraina-hadir-virtual-di-g20-bahas-imbas-perang-hingga-penerbitan-uang-digital||||Menteri Keuangan Sri Mulyani memastikan kondisi yang kini dialami Sri Lanka, berbeda dengan Indonesia.||||Sejauh ini, ekonomi domestik cenderung stabil akibat kemampuan APBN meredam guncangan ekonomi.||||Sri Lanka mengalami krisis ekonomi terburuk dalam sejarah, yang menyebabkan negara itu bangkrut.||||Sri Lanka tidak mampu membayar utang luar negeri yang mencapai lebih dari Rp754 triliun.||||Pemerintah Sri Lanka juga kehabisan dollar, sehingga tidak mampu membiayai impor barang-barang pokok, termasuk BBM.||||Kondisi ini memicu ratusan ribuan warga turun ke jalan dan masuk ke Istana Kepresidenan di Ibu Kota Kolombo.||||Massa menuntut Presiden Gotabaya Rajapaksa mengundurkan diri.||||Namun sebelum mengundurkan diri, Gotabaya dan keluarga melarikan diri ke Maladewa dengan menggunakan pesawat militer. |||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309112/bahas-krisis-ekonomi-sri-lanka-di-g20-sri-mulyani-pastikan-ekonomi-domestik-cenderung-stabil
tags: ekonomi indonesia stabil|g20|isu ekonomi global|krisis ekonomi sri lanka|nusa dua bali|sri mulyani

title: NEVER TOO SMALL: Artistâ€™s Tiny Beach Shack Australia - 30sqm/323sqf
description: Use code 15NTSDEAL to get 15% OFF your Meyer Labs cookware now following this link: https://bit.ly/NTSxMEY_V1|Located in the small coastal village of Walkerville, 2.5hours south east of Melbourne, architect Imogen Puller has designed a simple beach shack with adaptable spaces, multifunctional furniture and ample storage. Built to withstand the risk of bushfires and seaside corrosion, the exterior is wrapped in non combustible fiber cement sheeting, with rusted metal corten used for the decking. A unique mural on the facade is a nod to the ownerâ€™s artist agency. Built to passive house principles; an air tight envelope and high insulation levels in the floors, walls and ceilings, ensure an energy efficient and thermally comfortable home. The interior is a more minimal and calming space with light lime washed ply interior and light grey porcelain tile flooring. In the living come dining area, a custom designed banquette seat for the dining table unfolds to become a double bed, another daybed built neatly tucked under the stairs.The main bedroom is located in the voluminous upstairs space, where a queen storage bed and modular adjustable storage system make for a comfortable and adaptable space.|#tinyhome #architecture #interiordesign |Music: Enlightened One by E J R M|Produced by New Mac Video Agency|Creator: Colin Chee|Camera Operator: Nam Tran|Producer: Lindsay Barnard|Editor: Jessica Ruasol

description: Las fiestas de San FermÃ­n 2022 llegan a su fin este jueves con el octavo encierro, en el que los toros de la ganaderÃ­a Miura han perseguido a cientos de corredores por las calles de Pamplona en un recorrido rÃ¡pido, de dos minutos y diecisÃ©is segundos. El segundo encierro mÃ¡s corto de las fiestas despuÃ©s del de ayer, que durÃ³ dos segundos menos. Los mozos los han tenido difÃ­cil para ponerse delante de los toros en los primeros compases del encierro. Al llegar al Ayuntamiento los cabestros seguÃ­an en cabeza y no se han visto especiales incidencias, y asÃ­ han cubierto tambiÃ©n el tramo de Mercaderes. La manada ha tomado la curva sin incidencia, sin resbalones de los morlacos, que han enfilado velozmente la calle Estafeta.|Al inicio de Estafeta se han visto caÃ­das y la manada ha comenzado a estirarse hasta dividirse en dos grupos de tres toros. En el hueco producido entre ambos grupos, y a mitad de la calle, se ha producido una caÃ­da de varios mozos que trataban de ocupar ese espacio, que ha ido creciendo con el paso de los segundos, dando mayores opciones de inserciÃ³n a los corredores. Las caÃ­das se ha reproducido en adelante, pero sin embestidas de los animales. title: Hyderabadi Veg Muton Dum Biriyani - No Meat Goat Biriyani Recipe | Authentic Veg Mutton Dum Biryani
description: full recipe: https://hebbarskitchen.com/hyderabadi-veg-mutton-biryani-recipe/|@Hebbars Kitchen Hindi @Hebbars Kitchen Originals |hyderabadi veg mutton biryani recipe | veg mutton dum biryani | veg goat biryani with detailed photo and video recipe. Basically, a vegetarian or meat-free biriyani recipe prepared with a meat alternative. It carries the same meat-like texture with the same set of spices and can be served as a mutton biriyani alternative. The biriyani masala and the meat alternative is marinated with the same technique as the goat biriyani and then later cooked in dum style for an authentic taste.|hyderabadi veg mutton biryani recipe | veg mutton dum biryani | veg goat biryani with step-by-step photo and video recipe. Biriyani recipes have always been synonymous with the choice of meat used in it. However, there have been so many vegetarian alternatives with potatoes, paneer, mushroom and soya for non-meat eaters. But there has always been an argument, that it is not even close to authentic taste. Well, this meat-free mutton biriyani is not an answer to it, but certainly an alternative to meat-based biryani.|#hebbarskitchen

title: Is it a Model 3 killer? (Hyundai Ioniq 6 review walkaround)
description: Full details on the new 2023 Hyundai Ioniq 6, launching in Australia in the first half of next year and Europe and Korea sooner than that. |Underneath the Streamliner design, the Ioniq 6 uses the same e-GMP platform as the popular Ioniq 5 SUV, and has a 77.4kWh battery. But because the aerodynamics are so much better the Ioniq 6 will have a WLTP range of 610km in RWD 168kW trim. As tested here, with 239kW dual motor AWD and 20s, real range will land around 530km we estimate. |Priced between $70,000-$80,000 in Australia the Ioniq 6 will go up against the Tesla Model 3 and Polestar 2 in Australia as well as the BMW i4.|As always, we donâ€™t accept advertising from car manufacturers, and weâ€™re powered by Budget Direct - so this is an independent, honest review of the Hyundai Ioniq 6.|Subscribe now! https://www.youtube.com/user/ChasingCarsAustralia?sub_confirmation=1|More Hyundai content: https://www.chasingcars.com.au/Hyundai/  |Chasing Cars on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/chasingcarsaustralia/ |Follow Chasing Cars on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/chasingcars.com.au/ |Chasing Cars is Australia's most independent source of new car reviews, car industry news, comparisons and car guides. title: More damning revelations about Donald Trump at the inquiry into the January 6th Capitol riots | 7.30
description: The legal jeopardy for former US President Donald Trump went up another notch this week. At the latest public hearings of the January 6 committee, there were revelations of what Trump knew about plans to march on the Capitol, what he said publicly, and what he concealed, and details have emerged about what's being called the wildest meeting of his presidency. Neal Katyal is a prominent US lawyer, and he was watching the testimony in Washington. title: Ronny Jackson publicly criticized Biden's health. Then he heard from Obama
description: Former President Barack Obama sent an email to Ronny Jackson, a former White House physician who went on to become a GOP congressman, expressing his "disappointment" for his criticism of Joe Biden's cognitive health in 2020, according to a copy of the email obtained by CNN.|Obama sent the email, which Fox News first reported, when Biden was running for president and Jackson was running for Congress in Texas. Jackson retweeted a video of Biden with the message: "Remember the cognitive test that I gave @realDonaldTrump? The one he aced! Sounds like somebody else might need some testing done!! Scary!!"|Jackson received an email from Obama shortly after. The email is included in Jackson's yet-to-be-released memoir titled "Holding the Line: A Lifetime of Defending Democracy and American Values." #donlemontonight #CNN #News

title: 'Putin's economic shock...': Ukrainian Pres claims Russian behind Sri Lanka's unrest | Details
description: As unrest in Sri Lanka continues, a war of word between Ukraine & Russia has escalated. In the latest, Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky has blamed Russia for the crisis in island nation Sri Lanka. Zelensky said the economic shock after Putin's invasion of Ukraine triggered instability in crisis-hit Sri Lanka. Remember, Colombo used to import 45% of wheat from war-hit Ukraine. Lanka's more than half of soybeans, sunflower oil, peas & asbestos also comes from Russia and Ukraine. Crude oil prices are also on a high amid the UKraine-Russia conflict. Watch this report for more details.|#zelensky #putin #srilanka #ukraine #ukrainerussiawar #ukrainewar #srilanka #colombo #lanka #gotabayarajapaksa #ranilwickremesinghe #military #politics #economy #protests #srilankacrisis #economiccrisis

title: Momen Presiden Jokowi Ambil Sumpah Perwira TNI-Polri 2022 di Istana
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Joko Widodo melantik Perwira Tentara Nasional Indonesia (TNI) dan Kepolisian Negara Republik Indonesia (Polri) Tahun 2022, Halaman Depan Istana Merdeka, Kamis (14/7/2022).||||Dalam upacara tersebut, Jokowi juga memimpin pembacaan sumpah perwakilan perwira TNI-Polri. Jokowi juga menyematkan tanda penghargaan kepada empat orang peraih Adhi Makayasa tahun 2022.||||Baca Juga Lantik Perwira TNI-Polri 2022, Jokowi: Kedepankan Integritas, Kepentingan Negara di atas Segalanya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308987/lantik-perwira-tni-polri-2022-jokowi-kedepankan-integritas-kepentingan-negara-di-atas-segalanya||||"Bahwa saya akan memenuhi kewajiban perwira dengan sebaik-baiknya terhadap bangsa Indonesia dan Negara Kesatuan Republik Indonesia yang berdasarkan Pancasila dan Undang-Undang Dasar Negara Republik Indonesia Tahun 1945," kata Presiden Jokowi diikuti para perwira TNI-Polri.||||"Khusus perwira TNI, bahwa saya akan menegakkan harkat dan martabat perwira serta menjunjung tinggi sumpah prajurit dan sapta marga," ujar Presiden Jokowi.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309016/momen-presiden-jokowi-ambil-sumpah-perwira-tni-polri-2022-di-istana

title: Beredar Video Irjen Ferdy Sambo Menangis Peluk Kapolda Irjen Fadil di Tengah Kasus Penembakan
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV - Beredar sebuah video singkat yang memperlihatkan Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo memeluk erat Kapolda Metro Jaya Irjen Fadil Imran.||||Dalam video nampak Kapolda Irjen Fadil Imran yang datang masuk ke ruangan langsung disambut peluk oleh Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Isak Tangis pun ditampakkan Ferdy Sambo seraya pelukan Kapolda yang makin erat.||||Baca Juga Psikolog Ungkap Kondisi Terkini Istri Irjen Ferdy Sambo: Masih Syok, Alami Gangguan Tidur & Makan! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308927/psikolog-ungkap-kondisi-terkini-istri-irjen-ferdy-sambo-masih-syok-alami-gangguan-tidur-makan||||Video beredar di tengah sorotan publik terkait kasus penembakan Brigadir J di rumah Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Namun hingga saat ini belum ada keterangan mengenai video tersebut.||||Ferdy Sambo pun hingga kini belum memberi keterangan terkait insiden polisi tembak polisi yang terjadi di rumahnya.||||Kapolres Jakarta Selatan sebelumnya menyebut aksi penembakan berawal dari pelecehan Brigadir J pada istri Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Di tengah perkembangan kasus tersebut dan pertanyaan publik tentang di mana Ferdy Sambo, beredar sebuah video singkat yang memperlihatkan Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo memeluk erat Kapolda Metro Jaya Irjen Fadil Imran. ||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309053/beredar-video-irjen-ferdy-sambo-peluk-kapolda-metro-jaya-di-tengah-kasus-penembakan

title: Loopmancer Review
description: Loopmancer reviewed by Justin Koreis on PC. Also available on PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch. Loopmancer is a great roguelite. Repeating the same day over and over again is anything but routine thanks to great combat, compelling progression, and consistently refreshed levels stocked with a huge variety of weapons and enemies. Even after dozens of loops I feel compelled to jump back in and see what random assortment of gear I end up with, and how quickly I can make it through to the end. This is a loop well worth getting caught in.|#IGN

title: Viral: Alert lady constable rescues passenger stuck in platform gap at Ahmedabad station I Watch
description: An alert lady cop saved a passenger's life at Ahmedabad station. Constable Mandakini Parmar pulled a passenger out of the gap between the railway platform and a train who got stuck while boarding. In the video, the passenger can be seen following a fellow female passenger, who successfully boarded the train, which was already in motion. However, another female passenger held on to train handle as she moved along with the train but was unable to get on to the footboard. After continuing to move with the train for a few seconds, the passengerâ€™s legs were stuck in the gap between the platform and the train. This is when the constable rushed & saved the passenger from being crushed. Watch this report for more.|#constable #ladysingham #cops #rpf #police #ladycop #ahemdabad #viral #trending #youtubetrend #youtubetrending

title: Gwent: Rogue Mage Review
description: Gwent: Rogue Mage reviewed by Leana Hafer on PC. This standalone expansion to Gwent, itself a spin-off from The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt, is a roguelike successor to Thronebreaker: The Witcher Tales. While the lighter story may not hit the same epic highs as Thronebreaker, its character-driven snippets are delivered with strong writing and voice acting. For fans of the Witcher universe and card battlers with wacky mechanics that upend the usual rules, it's a very enjoyable journey if you don't worry too much about the destination.|#IGN #Gaming

title: 7 Syarat untuk Membuat Sertifikat Tanah secara Gratis
description: KOMPAS.TV-Ternyata untuk mengurus sertifikat tanah, tidak semua orang wajib mengeluarkan biaya.||||Terdapat beberapa kategori masyarakat yang dibebankan tarif Rp 0 alias gratis untuk mengurus sertifikat tanah.||||Aturan tersebut tertuang dalam Peraturan Pemerintah (PP) Nomor 128 Tahun 2015 tentang Jenis dan Tarif atas Jenis Penerimaan Negara Bukan Pajak yang Berlaku pada Kementerian Agraria dan Tata Ruang / Badan Pertanahan Nasional atau ATR/BPN.||||Siapa Saja yang Termasuk Kategori Bisa Mengurus Sertifikat Tanah secara Gratis?||||Berdasarkan Pasal 22 ayat (2) PP Nomor 128 Tahun 2015 menyebutkan.||||Menyadur dari Indonesiabaik.id, tujuh kategori masyarakat yang dikenakan tarif Rp 0 atas jenis Penerimaan Negara Bukan Pajak (PNBP), antara lain:||||1.Masyarakat tidak mampu.||||2.Masyarakat yang termasuk dalam Program Pemerintah Bidang Perumahan Sederhana.||||3.Badan hukum yang bergerak di bidang keagamaan dan sosial yang penggunaan tanahnya untuk peribadatan, pesantren, panti asuhan, panti jompo, cagar budaya, situs atau tempat ziarah.||||4.Veteran, pensiunan PNS, purnawirawan TNI, purnawirawan Polri, dan suami/istri/janda/duda veteran/pensiunan PNS/purnawirawan TNI/purnawirawan Polri.||||5.Instansi pemerintah dan pemerintah daerah, untuk melaksanakan tugas dan fungsinya dan tidak bersifat profit.||||6.Wakif atau pihak (orang) yang mewakafkan harta bendanya.||||7.Masyarakat hukum adat.||||Layanan gratis yang dimaksud, seperti tercantum dalam Pasal 22 ayat (1) PP, terdapat 3 layanan pertanahan:||||1.Pertama, pelayanan pengukuran dan pemetaan batas bidang tanah.||||2.Kedua, pelayanan pemeriksaan tanah oleh panitia A atau petugas konstatasi.||||3.Ketiga, pelayanan pendaftaran tanah untuk pertama kali meliputi perpanjangan atau pembaruan Hak Guna Usaha (HGU), Hak Guna Bangunan (HGB), atau Hak Pakai Berjangka Waktu.||||Baca Juga Syarat dan Biaya Membuat Paspor untuk WNI di Indonesia di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308222/syarat-dan-biaya-membuat-paspor-untuk-wni-di-indonesia||||Editor Video & Grafis: Joshua Victor ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308947/7-syarat-untuk-membuat-sertifikat-tanah-secara-gratis
tags: cara mengurus sertifikat tanpa biaya|mengurus sertifikat tanah gratis ini syaratnya|siapa saja yang bisa gratis mengurus sertifikat tanah

title: Tawuran Dua Kelompok Massa
description: Diduga dipicu salah paham , dua kelompok massa di Bekasi , Jawa Barat , terlibat saling serang dengan menggunakan petasan dan batu . title: U.S. Inflation Rises To 9.1% In June, Highest Peak Since 1981
description: The U.S. is facing the highest inflation in 41 years. Inflation ballooned to 9.1 percent over the same month last year. The Federal Reserve is expected to raise interest rates again this month. Economists worry that to bring inflation under control, the Federal Reserve may have to engineer a recession. title: MTP NOW July 13 â€” Inflation woes; new Uvalde surveillance footage; Biden lands in the Middle East
description: As President Biden kicks off his trip through the Middle East, his administration is facing their biggest challenge at home with the pace of inflation rising at its highest point in 40 years. Carol Lee and Heather Boushey discuss the potential fallouts. Plus: Gut-wrenching surveillance footage from Uvalde shows police waiting in the hallway for long periods as shots ring out throughout the school. Antonia Hylton speaks with the victims' families, who express their anger, while former ATF Special Agent in Charge Jim Cavanaugh calls it "a lack of leadership and a lack of courage." Leigh Ann Caldwell, Margie Omero and Brad Todd join the panel to talk midterms. title: Top trade destinations for Donovan Mitchell, talks Adam Silver's comments on KD | NBA | THE HERD

Plus, the two talk the Utah Jazz, who are suddenly open to trading their lone superstar Donovan Mitchell. title: Biden's first Middle East trip as US president - What to expect? | DW News
description: Biden arrived in Tel Aviv, his first visit to Israel since becoming US President.   It's a visit the White House says would have happened earlier, had there been no pandemic standing in the way.  |Later this week, Biden will travel on to Saudi Arabia. It's a visit that would probably not be happening at all, had there been no war in Ukraine, no inflation and no skyrocketing fuel prices. On the campaign trail two years ago, Biden vowed to make Saudi Arabia a pariah -- saying the Saudi crown prince's role in the murder of journalist Jamal Khashoggi revealed a kindgom lacking any redeeming values. |President Biden's opinion may or may not have changed, but the realities of geopolitics certainly have. Biden now says he hopes to reorient, not rupture the US-Saudi relationship. In other words, he's hoping the Saudis agree to pump more oil onto the global market. It will be a delicate balancing act for the US President, making his visit to Israel look more like a walk in the park.  |Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch

title: â€œShut up or get out!â€: UK speaker tells unruly lawmakers while PM leaving with â€œhead held highâ€
description: Britain's House of Commons Speaker Lindsay Hoyle on Wednesday ordered two lawmakers belonging to the Scottish party Alba to leave the debating chamber just before â€œPrime Minister's Questionsâ€  on Wednesday for refusing to comply with his instructions.|The two members of Parliament shouted out as one of their Conservative counterparts stood to ask a question in the weekly â€œPrime Minister's Questionsâ€ session in Parliament's lower house.|Struggling to make himself heard above the loud talking by lawmakers, the visibly-angry Hoyle ordered them to leave the chamber.|"Neale Hanvey, I am now naming you and Kenny MacAskill to leave this chamber," Hoyle said, requesting them to be escorted out and warning that it might lead to them being suspended from the house.|British Prime Minister Boris Johnson was speaking in Parliament a week after he was forced to resign after losing the support of key government ministers and his lawmakers. |He said he will stand down once his Conservative party has chosen a new leader and he will leave with his â€œhead held high.â€|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8969102/boris-johnson-resigns-british-prime-minister/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #unitedkingdom #borisjohnson

title: Highlights: First Images from the James Webb Space Telescope (Official NASA Video)
description: NASA revealed the first five full-color images and spectrographic data from the world's most powerful space telescope, the James Webb Space Telescope, a partnership with ESA (European Space Agency), and CSA (Canadian Space Agency). The world got its first look at the full capabilities of the mission at a live event streamed from the agency's Goddard Space Flight Center in Greenbelt, Maryland, on July 12, 2022.|The event showcased these targets:|- Carina Nebula: A landscape speckled with glittering stars and cosmic cliffs|- Stephanâ€™s Quintet: An enormous mosaic with a visual grouping of five galaxies|- Southern Ring Nebula: A nebula with rings of gas and dust for thousands of years in all directions|- WASP 96-b: A distinct signature of water in the atmosphere of an exoplanet orbiting a distant Sun-like star|- SMACS 0723: The deepest and sharpest infrared image of the distant universe to date|The full set of the telescopeâ€™s first full-color images and spectroscopic data are available at: https://nasa.gov/webbfirstimages|Full-resolution images can be downloaded at: https://webbtelescope.org|Credit: NASA|Download Avail Link:|https://images.nasa.gov/details-First%20Images%20from%20the%20James%20Webb%20Space%20Telescope%20(Official%20NASA%20Highlights)|Production Credit:|Producer/Editor: Amy Leniarthtt

title: Chaos in Sri Lanka as president flees | DW News
description: Gotabaya Rajapaksa has fled Sri Lanka and landed in the Maldives, after failing to escape to his first choice destination, Dubai. The former president resigned on Wednesday, designating the prime minister, Ranil Wickremesinghe, as the new acting president. He has declared a state of emergency. A curfew. Police have deployed tear gas to disperse crowds of protesters still out on the streets. People do not seem ready to embrace the country's new leader.|The political crisis is hitting citizens at the pump with record high prices. In an effort to conserve fuel, the government is asking people to work from home and has closed schools. Restaurants have even switched to cooking meals with wood. title: We Broke Up
description: I can't believe we broke up.  This is heartbreaking.... |It all started When Rebecca Zamolo posted "Transforming Into a Superhero For My Daughter." description: Russiaâ€™s defence ministry has said its forces shot down four Ukrainian military jets in the Mykolaiv region of southern Ukraine. Russian artillery and rockets pounded the Ukrainian town of Bakhmut overnight and into morning of July 13. Donetsk governor Pavlo Kyrylenko said Russian forces were â€œconstantly shelling the entire free territory of Donetsk regionâ€. Kyiv said that Russian forces used multiple rocket launchers to attack settlements in Mykolaiv. Russian-backed separatists claim Ukraine fired several missiles at Luhansk from the High Mobility Artillery Rocket Systems (HIMARS). The UKâ€™s defence ministry claims several Russian-backed officials in occupied areas are now facing resistance from Ukrainians. Ukraine has ruled out ceding territory to Russia as part of any ceasefire deal and said no peace talks were underway. Ukraineâ€™s foreign minister Dmytro Kuleba reiterated their aim to liberate all territories, restore territorial integrity and full sovereignty. title: Which Prices Are Rising The Most As Inflation Hits 41 Year High
description: The newly released consumer price index for June shows that inflation was up 9.1% since June 2021, staying at its most rapid rate in over 40 years. Over the last 12 months, fuel and oil saw a 98% increase and energy increased by 41.6%, a main contributor to most rising prices of goods. title: Buntut Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi, Pengusutan Fakta Perlu Keterbukaan & Transparansi
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Kapolri Jenderal Listyo Sigit Prabowo buka suara terkait insiden baku tembak antara Brigadir J dan Bharada E.||||Polisi membentuk tim khusus untuk mengusut tuntas kasus tersebut.||||Penembakan terjadi pada Jumat, 8 Juli 2022 di Rumah Dinas Kadiv Propam Polri, Irjen Ferdy Sambo yang berada di Komplek Polri Duren Tiga, Jakarta Selatan.||||Polisi menyebut berdasarkan hasil olah TKP, terdapat 12 kali tembakan dalam peristiwa tersebut.||||Baca Juga Mahfud MD Sebut Ada Kejanggalan Dalam Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi: Harus Ditangani dengan Serius! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308893/mahfud-md-sebut-ada-kejanggalan-dalam-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi-harus-ditangani-dengan-serius||||Kapolri Jenderal Listyo Sigit Prabowo mengatakan, ada dua tindak pidana dalam kasus ini, yang pertama terkait percobaan pembunuhan dan kedua terkait kekerasan terhadap perempuan.||||Atas penganganan kasus ini Komnas HAM menyatakan belum akan terlibat.||||Komnas HAM menilai masih percaya kasus ini akan ditangani secara profesional oleh polisi.||||Pengungkapan secara transparan kasus penembakan polisi oleh polisi tentu kini ditunggu publik.||||Terlebih kasus ini telah melibatkan tim khusus yang dibentuk Kapolri.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308898/buntut-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi-pengusutan-fakta-perlu-keterbukaan-transparansi

title: Memilih Tak Terlibat Langsung, Komnas HAM Lakukan Penyelidikan Mandiri Terkait Baku Tembak Polisi
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Tim Khusus Pengusutan kasus polisi tembak polisi di Rumah Kadiv Propam Polri mulai melakukan penulusuran dengan mulai melakukan olah TKP hingga mendalami hasil otopsi.||||Inspektur Pengawasan Umum atau Irwasum Polri Komjen, Agung Budi Maryoto berjanji pengusutan kasus polisi tembak polisi oleh tim khusus  bakal terbuka ke masyarakat.||||Sementara itu, Komnas HAM memilih tak terlibat langsung dalam tim gabungan penyelidikan insiden baku tembak di Rumah Kadiv Propam Polri,  Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Baca Juga Komnas HAM Belum Perlu Bergabung dalam Pengusutan Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi, Ini Alasannya... di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308890/komnas-ham-belum-perlu-bergabung-dalam-pengusutan-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi-ini-alasannya||||Komnas HAM menyatakan akan melakukan penyelidikan secara mandiri guna memastikan proses hukum berjalan secara transparan dan akuntabel.||||Dalam olah TKP lanjutan pada Rabu (13/7/2022) siang, Petugas Inafis Polri tampak membawa tiga buah koper dari dari dalam rumah.||||Selain Tim Inafis, petugas dari Satuan Reskrim Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan, Tim Pusdokkes dan Forensik Polri ikut mengawal jalannya olah TKP di lokasi baku tembak antara Bharada "E" dan Brigadir Yosua Hutabarat.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308920/memilih-tak-terlibat-langsung-komnas-ham-lakukan-penyelidikan-mandiri-terkait-baku-tembak-polisi

description: Raheem Sterling has joined Chelsea, bringing an end a magnificent seven-year stay with City.  |Sterling established himself as one of the Clubâ€™s greatest modern-day players during that period, making 339 appearances and scoring 131 goals.  |His 91 Premier League goals are second only to Sergio Aguero, and he exits the Club as our 11th highest goal-scorer of all time (all competitions) â€“ just one goal behind equal ninth-placed Fred Tilson and Billy Gillespie on 132. |Sterling is our second-highest scorer of all-time in European football, with 24 Champions League goals second (again) to Agueroâ€™s 43. |Sterling joined City from Liverpool in July 2015, in a deal that saw him become the most expensive English signing ever at that stage. |On signing, Sterling said: â€œmy mum said Iâ€™d look good in blue!â€ |He made his debut a month later in a 3-0 win away to West Brom and scored his first City goal against Watford at the end of August. |Of the many memorable moments of his career with City, his winning goal deep into added time away to Bournemouth in August 2017 will stick in the mind of those who witnessed his celebration with the travelling fans and subsequent sending off moments later for a second bookable offence. |Few will forget another dramatic winner he scored against Southampton three months later, with his 96th-minute goal securing a 2-1 win and extended Cityâ€™s winning run to 12 Premier League wins in succession â€“ a new Club record at the time. |City went on to win the title that season, earning 100 points in a campaign that saw Pep Guardiolaâ€™s men break numerous top flight records. |Sterling played his part to the full, scoring 23 goals in 45 games â€“ he also had his first Premier League winnerâ€™s medal to go with the Carabao Cup triumph earlier in the season. |The 2018/19 campaign arguably saw Sterling at the very peak of his powers as City recorded a domestic treble of the Premier League, FA Cup and Carabao Cup. |He made 51 appearances that season, scoring 25 goals along the way â€“ not including the winning penalty in the Carabao Cup final shoot-out success against Chelsea. |City would pip Sterlingâ€™s old club Liverpool to the title by one point, and his two goals in the FA Cup final win over Watford saw him named the PFA Young Player of the Year and Football Writersâ€™ Player of the Year. |The following season saw his best return yet 31 goals from 52 appearances and though the Premier League title went to Anfield, he added the FA Community Shield and another Carabao Cup success to his winnerâ€™s medals collection. |Raheem would add another 31 goals in 96 appearances over the two campaigns that followed â€“ both ending with Premier League title triumphs. |In total, the 77-times capped England forward has won 10 trophies with City and was awarded the MBE in 2021 for his admirable work in highlighting and progressing racial equality. |A wonderful Club servant, title: TIGHT SQUEEZE! The Hennessey Mammoth 1,000hp Hypertruck Visits My Garage
description: The @Hennessey Performance Mammoth TRX 1,000hp hypertruck is at @The Shmuseum! It's bigger, faster, louder and crazier than the base TRX and in bright yellow even more so. This Mammoth is the same beast I drove in California, but it's time for a challenge on tight UK roads...|For the Mammoth, the Hennessey team take the RAM TRX and dial up the standard car's 6.2l Supercharged V8 from 707hp to a gigantic 1,000hp thanks to a new supercharger amongst many other tweaks. It's not only the power boost, but also the full kit for off-roading, new wheels and tyres, bumpers, bullbars and so much more.|However, it's personally quite exciting to drive the Mammoth on another continent, on a short list of cars I've driven on multiple continents alongside my Ford GT and AMG GT Black Series, plus drives in a grey Bugatti Chiron Pur Sport and a satin black Gemballa Mirage GT. Since I drove the Mammoth originally on an overcoast day in California, it's changed to be fully wrapped yellow, but this is where it gets interesting on much smaller UK roads where perhaps it's not exactly at home...|Significantly wider than even my Ford GT, the Mammoth is quite literally massive as the name suggests. And it turns out venturing to some country lanes is a recipe for a stressful time!|Thanks for watching, Tim||||Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:07 Walkaround|03:42 Remote Start-up|04:14 Mammoth First Drive|09:05 Country Lanes|13:17 Highway |16:48 Tunnel Time|17:46 Interior Tour|20:21 Wrap up|#Hennessey #Mammoth #TRX|Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Florida Police Track Down Wanted Man Livestreaming On Facebook, Find Drugs and Guns
description: The Volusia County Sherriff's Department in Florida released bodycam footage showing officers tracking down a wanted man who was livestreaming on Facebook on May 22, 2020. Timothy Munford was wanted by Marion County authorities, who notified Volusia County officers that he was in the area. Officers arrested the suspect without incident and recovered two firearms, two bags of marijuana, and a powder that tested positive for fentanyl from his vehicle. Munford was convicted on two felony charges and received two 18-month prison sentences on October 12, 2020. Munford was released from prison on December 27, 2021. |#Police #Bodycam #LawAndCrime |STAY UP-TO-DATE WITH THE LAW&CRIME NETWORK:|Watch Law&Crime Network on YouTubeTV: https://bit.ly/3td2e3y|Where To Watch Law&Crime Network: https://bit.ly/3akxLK5|Sign Up For Law&Crime's Daily Newsletter: https://bit.ly/LawandCrimeNewsletter|Read Fascinating Articles From Law&Crime Network: https://bit.ly/3td2Iqo|LAW&CRIME NETWORK SOCIAL MEDIA:|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lawandcrime/|Twitter: https://twitter.com/LawCrimeNetwork|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lawandcrime|Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/lawandcrimenetwork|TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@lawandcrime|LAW&CRIME NETWORK PODCASTS: https://lawandcrime.com/podcasts/|SUBSCRIBE TO ALL OF LAW&CRIME NETWORK YOUTUBE CHANNELS:|Main Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCz8K1occVvDTYDfFo7N5EZw|Channel B: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVXOqoOCYbi-iXChKAl6DTQ|Channel C: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXCLaaClAWQiTkl3pw9ZdLw|Channel D https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMV3pzWIhJGLYzoHyxBjjNw

title: Kompolnas: Kami Bekerja Secara Profesional, Kami Sadar Sebagian Publik Bersikap Skeptis
description: Kapolri Jenderal Listyo Sigit Prabowo mengumumkan telah membentuk tim khusus untuk memantau penanganan  kasus penembakan Brigadir J yang terjadi di rumah dinas Kadiv Propam Polri pada Jumat, 8 Juli lalu. Tim gabungan yang dibentuk di antaranya terdiri dari Kepolisian, Kompolnas dan Komnas HAM. Apakah nantinya tim gabungan ini bisa menghasilkan pengungkapan yang sebenarnya terjadi di balik kasus penembakan antara dua polisi di rumah dinas Irjen Ferdy Sambo? Untuk membahasnya, Anchor Reza Helmi telah berdiskusi melalui sambungan zoom bersama Irjen Pol (Purn) Benny Mamoto - Ketua Harian Kompolnas

title: Texas school shooting: US cops waited in hallway as gunman fired at kids inside | Watch
description: If the Texas school shooting was not traumatic enough, this new video released by a local newspaper will send chills down your spine. The surveillance camera video shows how the gunman fired 100 rounds of shots as cops waited in the hallway while more reinforcements arrived, including officers armed with semi-automatic weapons and ballistic shields. The video shows how several police officers were present on the spot as the shooter killed 19 students & 2 teachers. The officers eventually stormed the classroom after one hour and 14 minutes and killed the gunman. Watch this shocking truth of America's worst school shooting in a decade.

title: 'Desi' 10 Downing Street: Anand Mahindraâ€™s meme on Rishi Sunakâ€™s UK PM bid goes viral
description: Anand Mahindra's 'desi' humour on UK PM race is winning hearts online. The industrialist shared a viral meme that tried to capture what it might look like if any Indian ever resided at 10 Downing Street, the official residence of the British Prime Minister. The entire picture was typical of a 'Griha Parvesh', or a ceremony performed at entering a new home, and was a not-so-subtle hint at the identity of the United Kingdom's possible new leader - Indian-origin British MP Rishi Sunak. Watch this video for more details.|#anandmahindra #twitter #viral #trending #ukpm #rishisunak #suellabraverman #britishpm

title: Mahfud MD Sebut Banyak Kejanggalan dalam Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi yang Tewaskan Brigadir J
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Menko Polhukam Mahfud MD mengatakan banyak kejanggalan dalam penanganan kasus polisi tembak polisi yang menewaskan Brigadir J akibat baku tembak di rumah Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Hal itu dikatakan dalam keterangan tertulis yang diposting dalam akun Instagram miliknya, Rabu (13/7).||||"Kasus ini memang tak bisa dibiarkan mengalir begitu saja karena banyak kejanggalan yang muncul dari proses penanganan maupun penjelasan Polri sendiri yang tidak jelas, hubungan antara sebab dan akibat setiap rantai peristiwanya," tulis Mahfud seperti dikutip dari akun Instagram miliknya, @mohmahfudmd, Rabu (13/7).||||Lebih lanjut, Mahfud mengapresiasi langkah Kapolri Listyo Sigit Prabowo dengan membentuk tim investigasi untuk mengungkap kasus tersebut.||||Baca Juga Polri Minta Keluarga Mendiang Brigadir J Melapor Terkait Peretasan Akun WA dan Media Sosial di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308839/polri-minta-keluarga-mendiang-brigadir-j-melapor-terkait-peretasan-akun-wa-dan-media-sosial||||Menurutnya, langkah itu sudah mewakili sikap pemerintah. "Itu sudah mewakili sikap dan langkah Pemerintah sehingga Kemenko Polhukam akan mengawalnya." Katanya.||||Di sisi lain, Mahfud MD menegaskan bahwa kredibilitas Polri dan Pemerintah menjadi taruhan dalam kasus tersebut.||||"Kredibilitas POLRI dan Pemerintah menjadi taruhan dalam kasus ini, sebab dalam lebih dari setahun terakhir, POLRI selalu mendapat penilaian atau persepsi positif yang tinggi dari publik, sesuai hasil berbagai lembagai survei." Katanya.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308863/mahfud-md-sebut-banyak-kejanggalan-dalam-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi-yang-tewaskan-brigadir-j

title: Intel Arc A380 Gaming GPU Review & Benchmarks vs. AMD RX 6400, GTX 1650, & More
description: Sponsor: Get 10% off Squarespace purchases (https://geni.us/BqEpf)|This is our first Intel Arc GPU benchmark & review (other than the DG1) for a true gaming desktop video card from Intel. The Arc A380 competes with the AMD RX 6400 closest, maybe the GT 1630 (we'll see), and aims to be a $130-$150 card. The A380 launched only in China at first, but will very likely find its way into the rest of the world's markets. The Intel Arc A750 is coming next, and we have shots of that in this video, but we don't have a price target on it yet. description: Kyiv launched artillery barragesthat destroyed a Russian arms depot in Ukraine's southern Kherson region, Ukrainian military officials said.|Officials said that Ukraine carried out a "special operation" to free military captives in the region, which is under Russian control.|The strikes destroyed artillery, armored vehicles and a "warehouse with ammunition in the town of Nova Kakhovka, the officials said.|Russian-backed authorities in the occupied Kherson region accused Ukrainian forces of damaging civilian infrastructure and killing at least seven people.|"Warehouses were hit, as were shops, a pharmacy, petrol stations and even a church," the head of Moscow's civilian-military administration in the Kherson region, Vladimir Leontiev, said on Telegram.|The deputy head of the Russian-backed administration in Kherson, Ekaterina Gubareva, said Kyiv had used US-supplied long-range, precision artillery systems in the strikes on Nova Kakhovka.|"The occupiers have already felt very well what modern artillery is and they will not have a safe rear anywhere on our land," Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said in his evening address, referring to heavy weaponry supplied by the West.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #UkraineWar

title: J&K: ASI Mushtaq Lone's family battles â€˜terror associateâ€™ tag for their son at cop's funeral
description: Heart-breaking scenes were witnessed at the funeral of ASI Mushtaq Ahmad Lone who was shot down by terrorists in Srinagar. His family battled the loss of two sons with his death. Back in 2020, Mushtaq's son Aaquib was killed during a security operation a few kilometres from their home in Kulgam. The engineering graduate was termed 'terrorist associate' by the J&K police back then. On Tuesday evening, his police officer father Mushtaq Ahmad was leading a checkpoint at Lal Bazaar in Srinagar. Terrorists surfaced outside the GD Goenka School and started firing, killing the officer and injuring two other policemen. Watch this video for more details.|#srinagar #jkpolice #tribute #mushtaqahmadlone #terrorists #jammuandkashmir #kulgam #terrorassociate #cops

title: Terdakwa Pemerkosaan di Sekolah SPI Akhirnya Ditahan - LAPORAN KHUSUS
description: KOMPASTV - Selebgram Medina Zein dijemput paksa dan ditahan atas dua kasus dugaan ancaman kekerasan dan pencemaran nama baik. Medina juga dilaporkan atas sederet kasus dugaan penipuan yang kini tengah ditelusuri pihak kepolisian.||||Sorotan lainnya, drama panjang penangkapan tersangka kekerasan seksual di Pondok Pesantren Shiddiqiyah Jombang, Jawa Timur, akhirnya berakhir. Muhammad Subchi akhirnya ditahan di Rutan Kelas Satu Surabaya Medaeng, Sidoarjo, Jawa Timur.||||Lima simpatisan yang diduga merintangi penangkapan Bechi juga telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka.||||Sementara itu, terdakwa kasus kekerasan seksual Julianto Eka Putra yang sebelumnya masih bisa menghirup udara bebas kini akhirnya ditahan. Kasus kekerasan seksual yang menjerat motivator sekaligus pendiri sekolah Selamat Pagi Indonesia (SPI) di Batu, Malang, Jawa Timur, mencuat dan viral di media sosial. Pemerkosaan diduga telah terjadi berulang kali sejak 2009.||||Sorotan lainnya, peristiwa penembakan antara dua anggota polisi di rumah Kadiv Propam Polri diduga dilatarbelakangi pelecehan terhadap istri Kadiv Propam.||||Sementara itu, fenomena Citayam Fashion Week di kawasan Sudirman, Jakarta, turut menjadi perbincangan publik.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308827/terdakwa-pemerkosaan-di-sekolah-spi-akhirnya-ditahan-laporan-khusus

A unique and interesting vegetable-based chutney recipe prepared with fried okra and spices. It is typically prepared and served with morning breakfast recipes like idli and dosa, if not as a side dish to rice-based recipes. It is known for its thick, dense and fibre texture derived from the fresh okra and hence can also be served as simple vegetable curry with a choice of Indian Bread.|bhindi chutney recipe | Bendekayi chutney | Okra Chutney for idli & Dosa with step-by-step photo and video recipe. Chutney recipes are perhaps one the underrated recipes, yet an integral part of Indian cuisine. Generally, it is prepared with basic ingredients like coconut, chillies, herbs etc, but it can also be prepared with vegetables too. One such hugely popular Karnataka or Telugu cuisine-based chutney recipe is bhindi chutney or Bendakaya pachadi Recipe.|#hebbarskitchen

title: Risa Saraswati - IVANNA (Official Music Video)
description: Dikenal sebagai publik figur dengan kemampuan supranatural, Risa Saraswati kemudian menuangkannya dalam sebuah karya. IVANNA menjadi salah satu sosok hantu yang juga Risa tuliskan dalam bukunya, bakat tersebut ternyata banyak mencuri perhatian masyarakat. Hingga akhirnya bersama MD Pictures an MD Entertainment Company, IVANNA diangkat menjadi sebuah film.|Sama seperti judul filmnya, lagu IVANNA sudah rilis sebelumnya pada tahun 2018 lalu yang turut menjadi bagian dari film Danur 2: Maddah. Bercerita tentang sosok hantu IVANNA, lagu ini merupakan gambaran Risa saat bertemu dengan hantu Belanda yang agresif dan tidak menyenangkan. Rasa dendam IVANNA juga turut ditunjukkan dalam lagu ini. Bersama MD Musik Indonesia, Risa akan merilis music video IVANNA. Mewakili makna lagu ini, Risa tampil dengan nuansa hitam dan hiasan lilin yang menambah kesan horor. Pre-order here: https://OasisMusic.lnk.to/bhn25ID|â€˜Be Here Nowâ€™ was released on 21st August 1997 and followed the success of â€˜(Whatâ€™s The Story) Morning Glory?â€™, Oasisâ€™ biggest selling album and the record that broke them globally. The previous summer, Oasis played to more than 250,000 people over two nights at Knebworth, with an astounding 2.5 million people applying for tickets. Released at midnight on Thursday 21st August 1997, at a time when most albums were released on Monday, â€˜Be Here Nowâ€™ sold a staggering 400,000 copies on the first day in the UK, with 663,400 sales in just 3 days. "Aber wir haben schon fÃ¼r viele Menschen heute eine Notsituation - nicht, weil es eine Knappheit gibt, sondern weil die Preise explodiert sind", sagt er im ZDF-Morgenmagazin. "Wir kÃ¶nnen uns das in Deutschland nicht vorstellen, aber wir haben eine zunehmende soziale Polarisierung."|"Wir haben schon jetzt eine Krise", sagt Fratzscher weiter. Man habe in der Corona-Pandemie gesehen, dass die soziale Schere weiter aufginge, "beim Arbeitsmarkt, aber vor allem bei Gesundheit und Bildung", sagt Fratzscher und fordert rasches Handeln von der Politik.|_____|Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen fÃ¼r Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erklÃ¤ren die HintergrÃ¼nde und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. title: Ukrainian 7-Year-Old 'Let It Go' Singer Has Joyful Reunion With Susanna Reid | Good Morning Britain
description: She won the hearts of millions worldwide with her rendition of Let It Go from a bomb ravaged basement in Kyiv. 7 year old Amelia and her brother Misha, 15, escaped to Poland with their grandmother while mum Liliia and their father Roman, remained in  Ukraine - it was a story dramatically told to Susanna by Liliia when Susanna visited Poland and met them at the end of April. |Amelia has since become a symbol of Ukrainian spirit singing now on primetime television and to packed stadiums. She has also travelled to Monaco where she met - and sang - to Prince Rainier. title: Wickremesinghe takes over as acting Lankan President; Protesters turn Colombo streets into warzone
description: Roads in Colombo turn into battlefield as Ranil Wickremesinghe takes charge as Sri Lankan President after Gotabaya Rajapaksa fled the country. Dramatic visuals of protests have surfaced from outside Wickremesinghe's residence. Thousands of protesters have stormed the grand mansion seeking Wickremesinghe's resignation. There is total chaos in the Lankan capital. The Air Force choppers are flying low to disperse the crowd. However, the protesters are adamant and have refused to budge. title: Lanka President flees to Maldives on military jet; Rajapaksa expected to resign today
description: Sri Lanka's embattled president flew out of his country to the Maldives early Wednesday, in a probable prelude to his resignation after months of widespread protests against his island nation's worst-ever economic crisis. Gotabaya Rajapaksa had promised at the weekend to resign on Wednesday and clear the way for a "peaceful transition of power" after fleeing his official residence in Colombo just before tens of thousands of protesters overran it. As president, Rajapaksa enjoys immunity from arrest, and he is believed to have wanted to go abroad before stepping down to avoid the possibility of being detained. Watch this report for more details.|#gotabayarajapaksa #srilanka #srilankacrisis #latestnews #breaking #maldives

title: Imbas Kasus Julianto Eka Putra, Polisi Geledah Sekolah SPI: Ada Enam Orang Korban
description: BATU, KOMPAS TV  Tim Identifikasi Direskrim Polda Jatim datangi Sekolah Selamat Pagi Indonesia (SPI) di Batu, Rabu (13/7).||||Kedatangan polisi ke Sekolah SPI masih terkait dengan kasus yang menjerat seorang motivator bernama Julianto Eka Putra.||||Diketahui, JE atau Julianto Eka Putra merupakan salah satu pendiri dan petinggi sekolah tersebut.||||Baca Juga Disidangkan 19 Kali, Terdakwa Kekerasan Seksual Julianto Eka Putra Akhirnya Resmi Ditahan! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308506/disidangkan-19-kali-terdakwa-kekerasan-seksual-julianto-eka-putra-akhirnya-resmi-ditahan||||Penggeledahan Sekolah SPI merupakan limpahan dari Polda Bali, atas laporan perihal dugaan eksploitasi ekonomi.||||"Sementara yang kami dapat, ada enam orang yang menjadi korban daripada kasus eksploitasi ekonomi yang dilakukan oleh JE," ujar Kombes Dirmanto selaku Kabid Humas Polda Jatim.||||Adapun soal laporan ini, status Julianto Eka Putra masih merupakan terlapor.||||"Sejauh ini statusnya masih terlapor, memperkerjakan anak di bawah umur," lanjutnya.||||Nama Julianto Eka Putra ramai dibincangan usai dirinya menjadi tersangka kasus kekerasan seksual.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308707/imbas-kasus-julianto-eka-putra-polisi-geledah-sekolah-spi-ada-enam-orang-korban

title: Polisi Kembali Lakukan Olah TKP di Rumah Irjen Ferdy Sambo, Status Bharada E Masih Sebagai Saksi
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Setelah berlangsung hingga Rabu (13/07) dini hari, Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan, kembali menggelar olah TKP lanjutan di rumah Kadiv Propam Polri, pagi ini.||||Olah TKP juga mengerahkan petugas dari Puslabfor Mabes Polri.  ||||Baca Juga Kabareskrim Pimpin Olah TKP Penembakan Brigadir J oleh Bharada E di Rumdin Kadiv Propam Polri di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308622/kabareskrim-pimpin-olah-tkp-penembakan-brigadir-j-oleh-bharada-e-di-rumdin-kadiv-propam-polri||||Sejak pagi tadi, sejumlah anggota kepolisian Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan, kembali mendatangi rumah dinas Kadiv Propam Polri, Irjen Ferdy Sambo yang berada di Komplek Polri Duren Tiga, Jakarta Selatan.||||Diketahui, petugas kembali melakukan olah tempat kejadian perkara lanjutan, guna mengumpulkan alat bukti, terkait kasus penembakan Brigadir J oleh Bharada E.||||Selain Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan, petugas Puslabfor Mabes Polri juga dikerahkan dalam kegiatan ini.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308691/polisi-kembali-lakukan-olah-tkp-di-rumah-irjen-ferdy-sambo-status-bharada-e-masih-sebagai-saksi

description: After surviving a bus accident in which almost all her classmates die, Alma wakes up in a hospital with no memory of the incident... or of her past. Her house is full of memories that are not hers, and both amnesia and trauma cause her to experience night terrors and visions that she cannot clarify. With the help of her parents and friends, unknown to her, she will try to uncover the mystery surrounding the accident while struggling to recover her life and her identity. title: Madison Review
description: Reviewed by Tristan Ogilvie on PC. Also available on PlayStation and Xbox.|"Madison is a mostly thrilling trek through darkness, packed with challenging puzzles to solve and plenty of disturbing secrets to uncover. Its clever use of the cameraâ€™s flash and eerie audio design combined for plenty of anxious moments, so itâ€™s especially deflating that all that tension sometimes turns to tedium due to unnecessary inventory restrictions and tiresome backtracking. Yet even with these occasional momentum-stalling detours, Madison is still a creepy crawl through a twisted haunted house with enough genuine out-of-your-seat scares to leave you shaken like a Polaroid picture."

title: Polisi: Bharada E Penembak Nomor Satu, Keluarga: Brigadir J Sniper Khusus
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Polisi menyebut Bharada E yang menembak Brigadir J di rumah Kadiv Propam Polri Irjen Pol Ferdy Sambo merupakan penembak nomor satu di resimen pelopor.||||Kapolres Jakarta Selatan mengatakan hal ini berdasarkan komandan dari Bharada E.||||"Kami juga melakukan interogasi terhadap komandan Bharada RE bahwa Bharada RE ini sebagai pelatih vertical rescue dan di resimen pelopornya dia sebagai tim penembak nomor 1, kelas 1 di resimen pelopor, ini yang kami dapatkan," kata Budhi di Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan, Selasa (11/7).||||Baca Juga Demi Mencari Titik Terang Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi, Kapolri Bentuk Tim Khusus! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308686/demi-mencari-titik-terang-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi-kapolri-bentuk-tim-khusus||||Sementara itu, pihak keluarga Brigadir J yaitu Ayah korban mengatakan Brigadir J merupakan sniper khusus terbaik yang sering ditempatkan di titik-titik rawan saat lebaran.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308690/polisi-bharada-e-penembak-nomor-satu-keluarga-brigadir-j-sniper-khusus
tags: baharada e penembak|brigadir j ditembak bharada e|brigadir j sniper|penembakan brigadir j

description: Instant Pot Chicken Curry | Pressure Cooker Chicken Curry | Chicken Curry Recipe | How To Make Chicken Curry | Instant Pot Curry | Chicken Gravy Recipe | Chicken Recipe | Chicken Curry With Coconut Milk|Ingredients for Instant Pot Chicken Curry:|(Tsp- Teaspoon; Tbsp- Tablespoon )|- Chicken, curry cut with bones- 1 kg (2 lbs)|Whole Spices:|- Green Cardamom- 5-6|- Cloves- 5-6|- Cinnamon- 2|- Star Anise- 1.5 |Spice Powders: |- Turmeric Powder- 3/4 tsp|- Red Chilli Powder- 1 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 2 tsp|- Curry Powder- 3 tsp|- Garam Masala Powder- 3/4 tsp |Other Ingredients:|- Onions chopped - 3 medium (225 gms)|- Ginger Garlic paste- 3 tsp|- Tomatoes, sliced - 2 medium (150 gms)|- Green Chillies, slit- 3|- Coconut milk- 1 US cup, around 225 ml|- Oil- 4 tbsp|- Coriander leaves, chopped- 2-3 tbsp|Preparation:|- Chop the onions and slice the tomatoes. Also slit the green chillies and chop the coriander leaves.|- For the coconut milk, you can use readymade coconut milk available in tetrapack or can. You can also use coconut milk powder to be mixed in water and used.|Process : |- In case youâ€™re using an Instant Pot, choose the SautÃ© function (Normal) and keep at the default time of 30 mins. |- Now heat oil and add the whole spices. Give a stir and then add the chopped onions. Continue frying on the same heat for 9-10 mins till light brown. | (For Pressure Cooker or Pan/Kadhai, fry on medium heat for 10 mins till light brown.)|- Press the SautÃ© function to choose the heat level to â€œLessâ€.  Now add the Ginger Garlic paste, give a mix and fry on low heat for 2 mins. |( For Pressure Cooker/pan fry on low heat for 2 mins.)|- Add the chicken pieces, give a stir and change heat level to Normal by pressing the SautÃ© function. |- Stir and fry the chicken pieces for 2-3 mins till colour changes to white. |(For Pressure Cooker/pan, stir and fry on high heat for 2-3 mins till the colour has changed)|- Now add the spice powders and 3 tbsp water, mix and fry on Normal heat level for 3-4 mins. |(In case of Pressure Cooker/ pan, mix & fry on medium heat for 4 mins)|- Add the sliced tomatoes and 2 tsp salt and fry on Normal heat level for around 3 mins till tomatoes are soft. |(In case of Pressure Cooker/ pan, fry on medium heat for around 3 mins till tomatoes are soft.)|- Now add the coconut milk, 150 ml water and the slit green chillies and give a mix. |- Cancel SautÃ© function in instant pot. |For Instant Pot, |1. title: Jonathan Kuminga & Moses Moody Combine for 50 POINTS At NBA Summer League
description: The NBA G League is the NBA's official minor league. Fans can get a glimpse at the players, coaches and officials competing to ascend to the NBA's rank. title: Ketegasan Jokowi dan Komitmen Kapolri Soal Penembakan Brigadir J oleh Bharada E
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Jokowi menanggapi kasus polisi tembak polisi yang melibatkan Brigadir J dengan Bharada E.||||Penembakan ini terjadi di rumah dinas Kadiv Propam Polri, Jakarta Selatan pada 8 Juli 2022.||||Presiden Jokowi secara tegas mengatakan agar proses hukum harus dilakukan dalam kasus penembakan ini.||||"Ya proses hukum harus dilakukan," kata Jokowi kepada wartawan di Subang, Jawa Barat, Selasa (12/7/2022).||||Baca Juga Presiden Jokowi Minta Kasus Penembakan di Rumah Pejabat Polri Diproses Hukum di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308510/presiden-jokowi-minta-kasus-penembakan-di-rumah-pejabat-polri-diproses-hukum||||Sementara itu, kasus penembakan Brigadir J oleh Bharada E yang diduga karena pelecehan terhadap istri Kadiv Propam Polri diselidiki oleh Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan.||||Namun, Kapolri juga telah membentuk tim khusus untuk menginvestigasi kasus yang menewaskan Brigadir J. Hal ini sebagai bentuk komitmen Kapolri dalam penyelesaian kasus penembakan ini.||||"Saya telah membentuk tim khusus yang dipimpin Pak Wakapolri, Pak Irwasum, Pak Kabareskrim juga ada As SDM termasuk juga fungsi dari Provos dan Paminal," kata Listyo kepada wartawan di Mabes Polri, Selasa (12/7).||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308617/ketegasan-jokowi-dan-komitmen-kapolri-soal-penembakan-brigadir-j-oleh-bharada-e

title: 'Very sensitive': Jaishankar on Sri Lanka crisis and political asylum to Rajapaksa family
description: External Affairs Minister S Jaishankar described Sri Lanka situation as "very sensitive and very complicated" and said India's focus right now is on the economic aspects of the neighbouring country. The Minister said New Delhi's commitment and support is for the friendly people of the island nation and it wanted to help them to go through a very difficult phase of their life. When asked about the possibility of India offering asylum to key members of the erstwhile powerful Rajapaksa family, who were attempting to flee in the face of massive public anger against them for mishandling the economy that has left the country bankrupt, the Minister said India's focus right now is on the Sri Lankan economic situation and it was not involved in other matters. Watch this video for more.|#jaishankar #srilanka #india #economiccrisis #rajapaksa #rajapaksas #neighbours #worldnews #latestnews #asylum #lanka #lankanews #srilankacrisis

title: Jeje Citayam Fashion Week Buka Suara Usai Ditertibkan Petugas Akibat Jam Malam PPKM
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Petugas aparat tiga pilar Polisi dan TNI Senin malam (12/7) tertibkan kerumuman remaja di kolong Kendal Citayam Fashion Week.||||Imbauan dilakukan petugas untuk cegah penularan Covid-19, karena wilayah tersebut masih berstatus PPKM level 1.||||Petugas menertibkan kerumunan remaja, yang kerap nongkrong di kawasan tersebut dan dilabeli Citayam Fashion Week.||||Baca Juga Rawan Kejahatan, Polisi Bubarkan "Citayam Fashion Week" di Sudirman di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308577/rawan-kejahatan-polisi-bubarkan-citayam-fashion-week-di-sudirman||||Polisi menyebut beberapa waktu ke belakang remaja CItayam Fashion Week kerap berkumpul hingga larut malam.||||Salah satu remaja putri yang viral, Jasmine Latika atau Jeje buka suara perihal penertiban Citayam Fashion Week.||||Ia menyebut dirinya secara pribadi tidak melanggar, dan tidak membuang sampah sembarangan.||||"Jeje enggak pernah buang sampah sembarangan," ujar Jeje, Senin (12/7).||||"Buat temen-temen Jeje, tolong ya, di sini Jeje punya nama, kalau mau buang sampah di tempatnya," lanjutnya.||||Jeje juga sampaikan pesan pada teman-temannya agar patuh pada aturan dan protokol kesehatan yang diberlakukan.||||"Untuk waktu main juga, kalau bisa ikutin peraturan dan protokol," ucap Jeje.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308632/jeje-citayam-fashion-week-buka-suara-usai-ditertibkan-petugas-akibat-jam-malam-ppkm

title: PERTAMA KALI GEN HALILINTAR KETEMU AMEENA
description: Guys, jangan lupaa download PINTU yaa|https://pintuinstall.onelink.me/fjuG?pid=Affiliate%20Marketing&af_web_dp=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pintu.co.id&af_dp=pintu%3A%2F%2Fdashboard&c=PNT_GenHalilintar&af_adset=PNT_GenHalilintar&af_ad=PNT_GenHalilintar|Sebagai tanda syukur Anniversary 27 tahun, Gen & Halilintar membawa 11 anak dan team ke Amerika di akhir tahun 2019 menyambut 2020. Pada bulan Februari 2020 Gen Halilintar ke tanah air, dan melanjutkan  dengan ziarah Wali Songo di bumi Nusantara. Setelah itu sekeluarga Gen Halilintar berniat untuk Umroh bahkan sampai Haji berlama-lama di Mekah Madinah. Di akhir Februari Gen & Halilintar telah lebih dahulu berangkat ke negara transit yaitu Malaysia, tempat Gen Halilintar akan berlepas untuk Umrah.  |Pada 17 Maret 2020 anak2 telah berangkat menyusul Gen & Halilintar ke Malaysia untuk bersama2 menunaikan ibadah Umrah ke Mekah. Namun apalah daya pada 18 Maret 2020 Malaysia dan juga banyak negara lain telah melakukan Lockdown termasuk juga Saudi Arabia, sehingga niat Gen Halilintar untuk Umrah Ramadhan tertunda, dan memaksa Gen Halilintar utk stay di Malaysia untuk waktu yang panjang, hinggalah baru bisa menyambung perjalanan keluar dari Malaysia pada 15 Desember 2021 menuju Istanbul. |Syukur luar biasa Gen Halilintar dapat berkumpul keluarga besar pada Anniversary ke-28 di Turki, orang tua bersama 11 anak, menantu, dan besan, keluarga besar dan team. Ketika itu baru Turki yang terbuka tanpa karantina, memudahkan keluarga besar untuk berkumpul di sana. |Dari sanalah Gen Halilintar kemudian memenuhi undangan ke Dubai yang juga sudah terbuka tanpa karantina. Dari Dubai lah Gen Halilintar like the UNBROKEN ones, tidak pernah mundur terus maju berjuang shg akhirnya dapat memenuhi NIAT yang telah tertunda untuk dapat tetap BERANGKAT menunaikan HAJAT sekeluarga berlama2 di Mekah Madinah, dan tepat tiba di Madinah di bulan Ramadhan 1443H yg awalnya diniatkan pd 1441H.  |Syukur luar biasa Gen Halilintar dapat menunaikan Umrah Ramadhan sekeluarga, berhari raya di Madinah, bahkan berlama2 di Mekah Madinah hingga masuk musim Haji. title: Mass Effect And More Games Free For Prime Day | GameSpot News
description: A ton of games are free for Prime Day, more Call of Duty leaks, and a new Kirby game is announced.|#Gaming #CallofDuty #primeday |Looking for something to play this summer? Prime gaming has you covered with some awesome free games! Plus, Modern Warfare 2 leaks and a new Kirby title, all on todayâ€™s installment of GameSpot News!|Itâ€™s time to get your sci-fi on. Prime gaming is giving away a bunch of free titles, including Mass Effect Legendary Edition, Star Wars Jedi Knight 1 and 2, as well as Republic Commando, all four of which are some of the best science fiction video games ever.|Please go play Republic Commando and then go pester Lucasfilm to make another. Itâ€™s so, so good.|If thatâ€™s not your speed, maybe these racing titles will be. Need for Speed Heat and Grid Legends, a game that only came out a few months ago, are also included in the free Prime Gaming bundle, among a selection of other titles. You can check out the full list, as well as all the best Prime Day gaming deals at GameSpot.com|Call of Duty games just canâ€™t stop leaking, this time for the upcoming Modern Warfare II releasing this fall. While nothing has been confirmed, the images shared as a part of this new leak have been taken down via copyright claims.|The leak includes a list of killstreaks, perks, field upgrades, and modes that players can expect to find in the game, many of which have been featured in previous seriesâ€™ entries. The biggest revelation is a variant of the massive scale Ground War mode, which features 64 players duking it out on large maps with vehicular combat. The alternate version of the mode, entitled Ground War Bomb, will reportedly feature alongside the standard Ground War, which is making its return to Call of Duty for the first time since 2019â€™s Modern Warfare.|TIME CODES: |00:16 - Prime Day games|01:06 - Modern Warfare II leaks|01:58 - Kirby's Dream Buffet

title: Call for inquiry into claims SAS executed Afghan prisoners - BBC News
description: The former head of the UKâ€™s armed forces has said he expects a â€œthorough investigationâ€ after the BBC found evidence that elite SAS troops executed detainees and murdered unarmed people during their deployment in Afghanistan.|The SAS forces were hunting for bomb-makers on night raids  The BBCâ€™s Panorama programme spoke to eye-witnesses and saw military reports showing people were shot dead after surrendering, in 2010 and 2011.  Itâ€™s said that one SAS unit killed 54 people in suspicious circumstances. |Lord Richards, the former Chief of the Defence Staff, said the allegations were â€œworryingâ€ and he had no doubt that the current head of British armed forces would want to investigate them.|The UK Ministry of Defence said it would always hold UK troops to â€œthe highest standardsâ€ and that they had served with courage and professionalism in Afghanistan. |Huw Edwards presents a BBC News at Ten special report by Panoramaâ€™s Richard Bilton.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: TOM DAVIES x DOMINIC CALVERT-LEWIN | EVERTON IN THE USA: EPISODE ONE

title: January 6 hearing recap: Trump's links to far-right extremists
description: The latest hearing from the House select committee investigating the January 6th, 2021, insurrection fleshed out the links between former President Donald Trump and the far-right extremist groups that were at the vanguard of the violent effort to stop the transition of power and keep him in office, despite his election loss.|The hearing focused on the loose affiliations between Trump, his informal political advisers, and members of far-right militia groups like the Oath Keepers and the Proud Boys.|The committee walked through snippets of witness depositions, court documents, previously unseen emails, and other materials to make the case that Trump coyly courted these militants and saw them as his troops on the ground to pressure Congress to overturn the 2020 election. #january62021   #thesituationroom #CNN
tags: latest News|Happening Now|CNN|january 6 2022|politics|us news|the situation room|donald trump

title: Florida Police Arrest High Schooler Who Brought Handgun to School
description: The Volusia County Sheriff's Department in Florida released bodycam footage showing the Atlantic High School resource deputy arresting a 16-year-old boy for bringing a loaded handgun to school on March 8, 2022. Police received a tip about a TikTok post showing the boy with a gun at school. Upon searching the boy, the deputy found a handgun tucked into his waistband. The suspect, who stole the firearm from a relative, is being charged with possession of a firearm on school property, grand theft of a firearm and carrying a concealed firearm. title: New Coup Evidence: Jan 6 Organizer Says Trump Took Violent â€œSideâ€ In Rally Clash
description: A top Jan. 6 rally organizer who has testified to Congress, Dustin Stockton, recounts the "split" within rally planners about whether Jan. 6th was going to be a rally to present information or a "radical" and violent day. Questioned by MSNBC's Ari Melber, Stockton says it became clear Trump had "taken that more radical side" by sending rally attendees to the Capitol, adding it "felt like an affront to us." title: WATCH: Former Oath Keeper spokesperson fears for next election cycle if Trump runs for office
description: Jason Van Tatenhove, former spokesperson for the far-right military group the Oath Keepers, testified on July 12 as the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack presented its findings to the public. The focus of the hearing was on extremist far-right groups like the Proud Boys and the Oath Keepers and the role they played in the Capitol insurrection.|He spoke about his view that the group hoped to become a paramilitary force. Rep. Jamie Raskin, D-Md., asked Van Tatenhove about whether the group had discussed committing violence against elected political leaders. Van Tatenhove said the Oath Keepers leader he spoke with wanted to make up a deck of cards of â€œkey players that they wanted to take out,â€ similar to military cards, which Van Tatenhove did not do.|â€œI do fear for this next election cycle because who knows what that might bring? If a president that's willing to try to instill and encourage to whip up a civil war amongst his followers, using lies and deceit and snake oil, regardless of the human impact, what else is he going to do if he gets elected again? All bets are off at that point,â€ Van Tatenhove said. â€œAnd that's a scary notion.â€|In the year since its creation, the committee has conducted more than 1,000 interviews, seeking critical information and documents from people witness to, or involved in, the violence that day.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG  |Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour  |Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6  |Follow us: |TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@pbsnews  |Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour  |Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour |Subscribe: |PBS NewsHour podcasts: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/podcasts|Newsletters: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/subscribe

description: Prime Time With Ravish Kumar - July 12, 2022: On Tuesday, the Supreme Court said that we cannot be a 'police state', and that the government should consider bringing in a special bail act so that bail is the rule, and jail the exception. title: Terungkap, Kondisi Gudang Senapan Serbu & Peledak! - AIMAN
description: Melalui fitur Toyota Safety Sense (TSS), Toyota mencoba untuk mengurangi bahaya dalam berkendara bagi pengemudi maupun penumpang. https://bit.ly/3OvbQ1N||||KOMPASTV - Ribuan butir peluru kaliber 9 milimeter (mm) dan 7,62 mm, senjata api (senpi) bermerek AK 47 buatan Rusia, 1 dus detonator, dan satu kotak dinamit atau TNT, ditemukan di dalam gedung tua di Jalan Asia Afrika, Bandung, Senin (6/6), saat sedang direnovasi.||||Penemuan ini lantas dilaporkan pemilik gedung ke salah satu anggota TNI, yang kemudian melaporkannya ke BNPT (Badan Nasional Penanggulangan Terorisme). Unit Penjinak Bom Detasemen Gegana Brimob Polda Jabar pun meluncur ke lokasi untuk melakukan evakuasi.||||Satu bulan pasca penemuan, Polda Jabar masih mendalami kasus untuk mengungkap siapa pemilik bahan peledak dan senjata api tersebut.||||Namun diperoleh informasi, sebelumnya, gedung tua milik DKH atau Ingrid itu dihuni oleh keponakannya berinisial SAM alias Acing yang meninggal pada 3 Agustus 2021.||||Apa yang terjadi? Mengapa polisi begitu lama mengungkap kasus ini? Jurnalis senior Kompas TV, Aiman Witjaksono, menelusurinya.||||Mendatangi tempat kejadian perkara (TKP) di tengah kota Bandung, Jawa Barat, Aiman berhasil menemui sejumlah saksi kunci yang mengenal Acing, penghuni gedung sebelumnya.||||Aiman juga berhasil melihat kondisi rumah dan menemukan fakta-fakta penting. Fakta-fakta ini kemudian dikonfirmasi ke Kepolisian Daerah Jawa Barat.||||Benarkah ada bahaya besar di balik penemuan senjata dan ribuan amunisi ini? Apakah juga terkait terorisme, mengingat senjata dan peledak jamak digunakan kelompok bersenjata?||||Bersama Arfin Sudirman, peneliti intelijen dari Universita Padjajaran, Aiman membahasnya.||||Saksikan AIMAN episode Misteri Peledak, Senapan Serbu, & Ribuan Peluru, Senin, 11 Juli 2022, pukul 20.30 WIB, eksklusif di Kompas TV.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308366/terungkap-kondisi-gudang-senapan-serbu-peledak-aiman

title: Hagfish: The world's slimiest creatures - Noah R. Bressman and Douglas Fudge
description: Discover the extraordinary capabilities of hagfish, the slime-producing fish that has survived on Earth for over 300 million years.|--|In 2017, a truck screeched to a halt. One of its containers slid off, hit a car, and spilled its contentsâ€” thousands of kilograms of hagfish. The result of this accident was an absolute mess: the highway was coated in a thick slime that took the fire department 7 hours to clear.
