title: Sir Mo Farah reveals he was trafficked to the UK as a child - BBC News
description: Olympian Sir Mo Farah was brought to the UK illegally as a child and forced to work as a domestic servant, he has revealed.|The athlete has told the BBC he was given the name Mohamed Farah by those who flew him over from Djibouti. His real name is Hussein Abdi Kahin.|He was flown over from the East African country aged nine by a woman he had never met, and then made to look after another family's children, he says.|In a documentary by the BBC and Red Bull Studios, Sir Mo recalls the moment he found out his family were still alive after years of no contact.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: 5 Essential Regional Burgers You Need to Try | Burger Scholar Sessions
description: Burger Scholar George Motz is on a mission to make sure YOU appreciate the regional American hamburger! What you may or may not know is that there are many regional burger styles out there, each with their own unique history. Which is why we picked out 5 essential regional burgers you need to try: the Deep-Fried Burger from Tennessee, the Butter Burger from Wisconsin, the Goober Burger from Missouri, the Slugburger from Mississippi, and the Fried-Onion Burger from Oklahoma. Get ready to travel back in time and learn about recipes from 100 years ago. title: Beginilah Kronologi Kejadian Polisi Tembak Polisi yang Menewaskan Brigadir J...
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Polres Jakarta Selatan menyatakan telah melakukan olah tempat kejadian perkara atas penembakan polisi terhadap polisi di Rumah Kadiv Propam Polri, Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Kapolres Jakarta Selatan, Kombes Budi Herdi Susianto menyatakan proses hukum kasus yang menewaskan Brigadir Nopryansah Yosua Hutabarat atau Brigadir J dilakukan sesuai prosedur.||||Berdasarkan keterangan Polri, peristiwa penembakan di Rumah Kadiv Propam Polri terjadi pada 8 Juli lalu, Brigadir J disebut masuk ke kamar Istri Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo dan diduga melakukan pelecehan dan menodongkan senjata.||||Atas kejadian ini, istri Irjen Ferdy Sambo berteriak yang membuat Brigadir panik dan keluar kamar.||||Baca Juga Paman Brigadir J Meninggal Dunia Kena Serangan Jantung ketika Hendak Berikan Sambutan saat Melayat di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308528/paman-brigadir-j-meninggal-dunia-kena-serangan-jantung-ketika-hendak-berikan-sambutan-saat-melayat||||Setelah mendengar teriakan, Bharada E datang dan menanyakan apa yang terjadi namun dibalas dengan tembakan.||||Selanjutnya saling tembak terjadi yang menyebabkan Brigadir J tewas.||||Sementara itu, orang tua Brigadir Nopriyansah menyebut adanya sejumlah kejanggalan kasus penembakan putranya.||||Ayah Brigadir J menyebut sejumlah fakta yang disampaikan polisi patut dipertanyakan.||||Terkait dengan kasus penembakan di Rumah Kadiv Propam Polri, Ketua Komisi III DPR, Bambang Wuryanto menilai belum dibutuhkan penonaktifan Irjen Ferdy Sambo.||||Sementara itu, Indonesian Police Watch memandang perlu dibentuknya tim pencari fakta agar kasus ini terang benderang.||||Kasus penembakan ini tentu menjadi perhatian publik, terutama konsep Polri presisi dari Kapolri yang salah satu poinnya yakni transparansi berkeadilan.||||Publik tentu menantikan proses penyidikan yang transparan dalam kasus ini.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308541/beginilah-kronologi-kejadian-polisi-tembak-polisi-yang-menewaskan-brigadir-j

title: BMW Mâ€™s Secret CSLs Youâ€™ve Never Seen Before â€“ Part 2: V10 E60 M5 CSL + V10 E63 M6 CSL | Top Gear
description: Ever since BMWâ€™s M Division started business back in 1972, only three cars have ever officially worn the â€˜CSLâ€™ moniker. The original 3.0 CSL everyone of a certain age gets gooey over, the E46-generation M3 CSL that warms the dark heart of the internet, and the latest M4 CSL. However, there were four secret CSL prototypes that never saw the light of a Munich day, at least until now.|In part one, Top Gear Magazine's Ollie Marriage looked at an E46 M3 CSL with an E39-gen M5's V8 shoehorned under the bonnet, and a prototype F87 M2 CSL that featured elements from the M4 GTS. Here's a link in case you missed it: https://youtu.be/pNJokoum5aY |In this second part, Ollie looks at two secret CSLs from the generation of M that famously went hardcore: the E60 M5 and the E63 M6. Both shared a 5.0-litre naturally-aspirated V10 engine making them the most uncompromising M cars of the time. title: Presiden Jokowi Minta Kasus Penembakan di Rumah Pejabat Polri Diproses Hukum
description: KOMPAS.TV - Polisi terus mendalami kasus penembakan antar-anggotanya di rumah dinas Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo. Polisi belum menetapkan tersangka atas kasus ini.||||Di sela kunjungannya ke Subang, Jawa Barat, Presiden Joko Widodo angkat bicara soal kasus penembakan di rumah Kadiv Propam Polri. Presiden minta proses hukum dilakukan.||||Baca Juga Kapolri Jenderal Listyo Sigit Buka Suara Soal Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308455/kapolri-jenderal-listyo-sigit-buka-suara-soal-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi||||Polisi terus mendalami kasus penembakan antar-anggotanya di rumah Dinas Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo. Polisi belum menetapkan tersangka atas kasus ini.||||Sementara terkait tewasnya sang anak, ayah Brigadir J menuntut polisi mengusut tuntas kasusnya.||||Keluarga merasa ada kejanggalan dalam kematian anaknya. Di antaranya ditemukannya luka dan memar di tubuh Brigadir J.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308510/presiden-jokowi-minta-kasus-penembakan-di-rumah-pejabat-polri-diproses-hukum

title: Pro Chef Turns Canned Black Beans Into 3 Meals For Under $9 | The Smart Cook | Epicurious
description: Chef Dan Giusti is back with another edition of The Smart Cook, this time demonstrating the potential waiting within your average can of black beans. Watch as Dan prepares a day's worth of meals, each elevating canned black beans from the mundane to something nutritious and surprisingly delicious. The best part? All 3 dishes come in for under $3 a serving.||||Dan Giusti, formerly the head chef of Noma, is the founder of Brigaid, a company that places professional chefs into institutional food spaces like public schools. Brigaid chefs bring their experience, knowledge and technique to institutional kitchens to improve food quality. Similar to how Brigaid works--by bringing professional chefs into institutional spaces to apply their knowledge to new environments-- The Smart Cook intends to do the same by bringing Chef Dan's experience and knowhow into your home with delicious recipes prepared on a budget.||||Learn more atÂ https://www.chefsbrigaid.com/||||Follow Dan on Instagram at @dan.giusti and @brigaid|Still havenâ€™t subscribed to Epicurious on YouTube? â–ºâ–º http://bit.ly/epiyoutubesub||||ABOUT EPICURIOUS||Browse thousands of recipes and videos from Bon AppÃ©tit, Gourmet, and more. title: How SpaceX Could Win The Space Race | CNBC Marathon
description: CNBC Marathon explores SpaceX's quest to win the space race.|SpaceXâ€™s broadband satellite internet, Starlink, is expected to be a cash cow for SpaceX, bringing in as much as $30 billion a year â€” more than 10 times the annual revenue of its existing rocket business. This revenue will be used to fuel Starlink's CEO, Elon Muskâ€™s ultimate goal of building a colony on Mars. Eventually, Starlink may even keep us connected on the Red Planet.|To get real-life first impressions of the service, CNBC spoke to more than 50 people who have been using Starlink. Those surveyed included households in Canada and 13 U.S. states: California, Colorado, Idaho, Iowa, Maine, Michigan, Minnesota, Montana, Ohio, Oregon, Washington, Wisconsin and Wyoming.|Starship is SpaceXâ€™s largest reusable rocket. It can carry more than 100 metric tons of cargo and crew per launch. Musk, says Starship represents the â€œholy grailâ€ for space travel, but the giant rocket vehicle also is crucial for SpaceXâ€™s future. Some experts have estimated that if SpaceX succeeds with Starship alongside Starlink, the space firmâ€™s valuation could skyrocket into the trillions of dollars. But before SpaceX can get Starship into orbit, the company faces a number of technical and regulatory challenges.|The rocket business is heating up and one startup has grand ambitions of following SpaceX to orbit. With a team comprised of industry veterans, Firefly Aerospace wants to be a dominant launch provider in the growing small satellite market. While the rewards are great, the risk are high. The company already suffered through a bankruptcy and is still trying to reach orbit.|CNBC Marathon brings together the best of CNBC on YouTube.|Chapters:|00:00 Introduction|00:39 Why Starlink is crucial to SpaceXâ€™s success (Published April 2021)|19:46 Why Starship is the holy grail for SpaceX (Published March 2022)|34:33 How ex-SpaceX engineers are fueling the space race with Firefly (Published November 2021)|Subscribe to CNBC: http://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBC|About CNBC: From 'Wall Street' to 'Main Street' to award winning original documentaries and Reality TV series, CNBC has you covered. title: One J&K cop killed, 2 injured as terrorists fire indiscriminately at police in Srinagar's Lal Bazaar

title: Skoda Fabia review: how could VW let this happen?
description: The new Skoda Fabia has given Volkswagen a massive headache...here's why. |Read more at Auto Express: |New 2022 Skoda Fabia review: https://aex.ae/2JsMR2k|New 2022 Volkswagen Polo review: https://aex.ae/2yY6ffI|SUBSCRIBE for more new car reviews and Steve Sutcliffe track tests: http://aex.ae/2gY9ABE|Itâ€™s fair to say that todayâ€™s superminis are not the compact runabouts they once were. Always a popular choice for its mix of affordability, practicality and ease of use, the humble supermini has faced a new era of safety regulation, combined with buyers demanding improved quality, extra space and greater comfort. All of which has led to more sizeable models being designed and brought to market.|In fact, the breadth of skills on offer from established supermini rivals such as the Ford Fiesta, Renault Clio and Vauxhall Corsa mean that the gap between this segment and traditional family hatchbacks such as the Ford Focus and VW Golf is closer than ever. With extra competition from its SEAT Ibiza and Volkswagen Polo stablemates, and the likes of the Hyundai i20, Mazda 2, Peugeot 208 and Toyota Yaris offering strong appeal, Skodaâ€™s fourth-generation Fabia certainly has its work cut out.|Lucky then, that the five-door Czech supermini benefits from using the same MQB-A0 platform as its Polo and Ibiza cousins. This architecture also underpins Skodaâ€™s Scala family car and Kamiq small SUV, and its lightness helps to keep the Fabiaâ€™s weight roughly the same as its predecessorâ€™s. Sounds promising, but how does the Fabia compare to its arch nemesis, the Volkswagen Polo? Nicola Hume finds out.|More Auto Express videos: |Car reviews playlist: http://aex.ae/2gY4ViX|Track battle playlist: https://aex.ae/2U8yvdf|Car news playlist: https://aex.ae/3vyKA8G|Follow us|Twitter: https://twitter.com/AutoExpress|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AutoExpress|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/autoexpressmagazine

title: Jack Wilshere appointed Arsenal U18 Head Coach
description: We are delighted to announce the appointment of Mehmet Ali and Jack Wilshere as the new Head Coaches of our Under-21 and Under-18 sides, respectively.|Mehmet joined us as our Under-23s assistant coach back in January, and following a positive six months he will now take on the role of Head Coach for our Under-21s as well as our Professional Development Phase lead. |Max Porter will be joining Mehmetâ€™s team as the Under-21s assistant coach, following his promotion where he was previously assistant coach to our Under-18s. Max has been in the game for several years making over 300 appearances at clubs including Barnet, Rushden & Diamonds, Newport County and Chelmsford City. Max joined us in 2019, when he took up a full-time coaching role.|Jack, a former academy graduate who made 197 Arsenal appearances between 2008 and 2018, during which time he won the FA Cup in 2014 and 2015 and the FA Youth Cup in 2009, is back working at the club where he takes on his first role in coaching, as the Head Coach of our Under-18s. |Adam Birchall will join Jack as our new Under-18s assistant coach alongside his new role as Under-17s Head Coach, moving from his previous position as our Under-16s Head Coach. Adam developed through our academy as a player before joining Mansfield Town in 2005. Adam's playing career spanned 11 years and over 300 appearances at clubs including Mansfield Town, Barnet, Dover Athletic and Gillingham, during which time he also made 12 appearances for Wales Under-21s. In 2016 Adam re-joined us as a coach and has gained valuable experience throughout the age groups.|Talking about his new role, Mehmet said: â€œItâ€™s a great honour and privilege to be a part of this club and lead our Under-21s. Iâ€™ve already had six good months at the club, so Iâ€™ve got a sound understanding of the players. title: Sam Smith - The Making Of â€˜Love Me Moreâ€™ | Vevo Footnotes
description: Sam Smith - The Making Of "Love Me More" | Vevo Footnotes|"Feeling like the mirror isn't good for your health" - what great line to describe a bout with self-doubt, right? Sam Smith nailed that feel in "Love Me More."  It's such a personal song, the singer wanted to have a hand in shaping of the video, so he co-directed with his pal Luke Monaghan. Shutting down a London street for that opening scene,   shooting the dance club action at the Royal Vauxhall Tavern on Fentiman Road - Smith wanted to support queer spaces that give a safe homes to LGBTQ+ community, as well as show fans a bit of his London roots. He explained it all to our Footnotes crew. title: IPW: Usut Penembakan Brigadir J, Kadiv Propam Harus Non-Aktif Agar Penyelidikan Clear
description: Seorang Perwira Polisi Brigadir Nopryansyah Yosua Hutabarat tewas setelah terlibat baku tembak dengan rekannya Bharada E. Menurut Mabes Polri, penembakan dipicu pelecehan yang dilakukan Brigadir Josua terhadap istri Kadiv Propam Irjen Pol Ferdy Sambo di kediaman petinggi Polri tersebut. Namun pihak keluarga tidak terima dengan penjelasan Polisi yang dinilai janggal. Keluarga menuntut agar penyelidikan atas meninggalnya Brigadir Josua diusut tuntas.|Untuk membahasnya lebih dalam, simak pembahasan news anchor CNN Indonesia Rivana Pratiwi dengan Ketua Indonesia Police Watch Sugeng Teguh Santoso dan Anggota Komisi Tiga DPR Trimedya Panjaitan.

title: Keluarga Brigadir J: Josua Tidak Mungkin Melecehkan Istri Kadiv Propam
description: Keluarga Brigadir J, polisi yang tewas di rumah Kadiv Propam Mabes Polri, menilai keterangan polisi tentang penyebab kematian janggal. Karena tidak dibuktikan dengan rekaman CCTV. title: Martin vs Marinez HIGHLIGHTS: July 9, 2022 | PBC on Showtime
description: (July 9,2022) Unbeaten rising star Frank Martin (16-0, 12 KOs) showed the full complement of skills that has made him one of the most talked about up-and-comers in the 135-pound division, as he delivered a methodical destruction on his way to stopping Jackson MariÃ±ez (19-3, 7 KOs) in the 10th and final round.| |After a tentative first two rounds, the Derrick James-trained Martin began to use his superior footspeed to put himself into position to land his lethal left hand to the head and body.| |â€œI was ready to go the distance whether I got the knockout or not,â€ said Martin, whoâ€™s stablemate and promoter, unified welterweight world champion Errol Spence Jr. watched his victory ringside and later told Jim Gray of SHOWTIME that he expects to face WBO titleholder Terence Crawford in a blockbuster welterweight undisputed championship fight later this year. â€œMe and Derrick James worked hard in the gym. It was just a matter of me being patient and not being anxious.â€| |MariÃ±ez was able to use his size advantage over the early rounds to keep Martin honest, having success landing counter rights over the top of Martinâ€™s guard.| |â€œI felt great,â€ said MariÃ±ez. â€œI was very comfortable inside the ring. It would absolutely have been a different result had I had more than eight days to prepare.â€| |MariÃ±ez, who stepped in as a late replacement to face Martin, was unable to put together effective combinations and too often relied on single-punch counters. Martin was able to slowly break MariÃ±ez down with a consistent body attack, landing 53 shots there throughout the action. He also held advantages in both punches thrown (505-411) and punches landed (160-106).| |â€œIâ€™m just an accurate puncher,â€ said Martin. â€œWe had to really stay on the outside of the hook, I was doubling the two and trying to come inside with the hook.â€| |After a close first half of the fight, Martin began to pull away in the later rounds and finally broke through and hurt MariÃ±ez late in round nine. He connected on a series of vicious left hands that staggered MariÃ±ez, before a follow up attack left MariÃ±ez on the mat in the neutral corner.| |â€œThe knockdown in the ninth changed the tone of the fight,â€ said MariÃ±ez. â€œMaybe I could have been more careful. These things happen in boxing, and you just gotta be ready to roll with the punches. He had power, and so did I.â€| |MariÃ±ez was able to get to his feet and survive the round, but Martin wasted little time restarting his offense in round 10. He pushed the pace from the outset and rained blows onto MariÃ±ez, who was pinned against the ropes, until MariÃ±ez hit the canvas again and referee Rafael Ramos jumped in to end the fight 30 seconds into the round (watch highlight HERE).| |â€œI was on him once I had him hurt, I was hungry, he was in deep waters so I had to get him out of there,â€ said Martin. â€œIâ€™m right there with those top guys at lightweight, sit me at the table with them, whenever, Iâ€™m ready. Iâ€™m going to sit down with my team and hopefully get something big. At the end of the day weâ€™ve won them all.â€|#FrankMartin #MartinMarinez #JacksonMarinez|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: Thousands line streets of Tokyo to bid farewell to former Japanese PM Shinzo Abe
description: Thousands of mourners lined the streets of central Tokyo to bid farewell to former Japanese prime minister Shinzo Abe, who was assassinated on Friday while campaigning. His hearse was driven past political landmarks after a private funeral. The incident has rattled Japan and prompted an outpouring of international condemnation and grief. The Japanese government said it has received 1,700 letters of condolences from 259 countries and regions. title: 2023 Honda CR-V First Look | A Fresh Redesign for Honda's Small SUV | Price, Interior, Engine & More
description: The Honda CR-V has been one of the most popular small SUVs since its release back in 1997. In this video, Alistair Weaver from Edmunds brings you a first look at the completely redesigned 2023 Honda CR-V and talks about everything we know so far about Honda's compact SUV. Alistair runs down all of the changes in store for the 2023 CR-V, including how the new design looks, what new features to expect, and whether it will be offered with a third row. The Honda CR-V has been the go-to for drivers looking for a do-everything family SUV, and the redesigned 2023 CR-V is hoping to keep that trend going. This is our first look at the 2023 Honda CR-V.|2023 Honda CR-V price & review: https://edmu.in/3IjUnr7|00:00 Intro|00:27 Walk-around|02:05 Interior|05:23 Cargo & Engine|07:04 Edmunds' Take|Subscribe to Edmunds https://www.youtube.com/user/edmundsvideo?sub_confirmation=1 for the latest car news, car reviews, car comparisons, car shopping and advice. |Visit us! https://www.edmunds.com.

title: Kapolri Jenderal Listyo Sigit Buka Suara Soal Kasus Polisi Tembak Polisi
description: KOMPAS.TV - Peristiwa penembakan antara dua anggota polisi di rumah kadiv Propam Polri Irjen Ferdy Sambo dilatarbelakangi oleh pelecehan yang dilakukan Brigadir J terhadap istri Kadiv Propam.||||Baku tembak antara Brigadir J dan Bharada E mengakibatkan Brigadir J meninggal dunia.||||Baca Juga Polisi Akui Belum Ada Bukti Brigadir J Lakukan Pelecehan sebelum Tewas Ditembak di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308392/polisi-akui-belum-ada-bukti-brigadir-j-lakukan-pelecehan-sebelum-tewas-ditembak||||Karopenmas Divisi Humas Polri Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan menyebut, dalam olah TKP ditemukan beberapa temuan seperti luka tembak dan motif dari Bharada E yang melepaskan tembakan ke Brigadir J hingga tewas.||||Polisi menyebut pelecehan terhadap istri Irjen Sambo yang menjadi faktor utama baku tembak terjadi di rumah dinas kadiv propam tersebut.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308455/kapolri-jenderal-listyo-sigit-buka-suara-soal-kasus-polisi-tembak-polisi
tags: bharada e|brigadir j|kapolri|polisi tembak polisi|polri|tembak

title: Kerja Sambil Kampanye Anak, Mendag Ditegur Jokowi: Fokus Saja Stabilkan Harga Migor!
description: LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Joko Widodo menegur Menteri Perdagangan, Zulkifli Hasan agar fokus bekerja menstabilkan harga minyak goreng curah.||||Hal ini disampaikan Presiden merespons pernyataan Zulkifli Hasan yang meminta warga memilih anaknya saat membagikan minyak goreng gratis di Lampung.||||Pernyataan ini disampaikan Presiden Joko Widodo saat meninjau Pasar Sukamandi Di Kabupaten Subang, Jawa Barat.||||Baca Juga Demokrat: Perbuatan Zulkifli Hasan untuk Anaknya Sama dengan yang Dilakukan Jokowi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/308375/demokrat-perbuatan-zulkifli-hasan-untuk-anaknya-sama-dengan-yang-dilakukan-jokowi||||Presiden mengingatkan Zulkifli Hasan fokus menjalankan tugas yang diperintahkan, yakni menurunkan harga minyak goreng curah menjadi Rp 14.000 per liter.||||Sebelumnya, pada pekan lalu Menteri Perdagangan sekaligus Ketua Umum PAN, Zulkifli Hasan hadiri pasar murah minyak goreng yang digelar PAN di Teluk Betung Timur, Bandar Lampung.||||Sambil bagi-bagi minyak goreng gratis, Zulkifli mengajak warga memilih putrinya.||||Ia juga berjanji menggelar acara serupa rutin untuk warga.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308440/kerja-sambil-kampanye-anak-mendag-ditegur-jokowi-fokus-saja-stabilkan-harga-migor
